This application is divided into 3 projects.
MVCURLShortner client : 
Install Ninject from Nuget package manager (repository pattern to loosely couple controller and data entities)
Controller will be using URLShortner module to cut down the url.

URLShortnerModule : 
Map the domain class with the database
In service folder, create interface and class for the logic to shorten the url
The shortnerservice , referes to IdEncoder which is having the main logic to encode and decode the url.

Test Project : 
nunit test project with encoding and decoding logic.
